{"tid":2099493,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來已經有人因失業自殺","createTime":"2020-07-08T09:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:23:31.000Z","uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29b224bce71794ddcbe93601d377a8be33187039","tid":2099493,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"失業問題困擾 中年漢大窩口邨墮斃<br />\n<br />\n葵涌一名近日疑受失業問題困擾的48歲男子，昨日傍晚從大窩口邨富秀樓一單位墮斃。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日傍晚6時39分接獲途人報案，發現事主倒臥富秀樓對開，懷疑從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主當場被證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信從一單位墮下。事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。"},{"pid":"8dad48fe979715e16a114176efe80e758e0edd9a","tid":2099493,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"48歲（失業）<br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5664803db10a2a5cab365103db23eb280bf1ede","tid":2099493,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"癡撚線世界"},{"pid":"0c7d3a379f7df17c4ee0fa61cb74a0c6a6786112","tid":2099493,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"真係同失業有關?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aedfec49beb4d581d8d85242074233bbd6f8b7","tid":2099493,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"其實得罪政府唔係咩大件事，點解要攪到人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3a35fb748db784fe873cd8eee19c5af3c8650b","tid":2099493,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"之前又一城有個東主已經財困自殺左"},{"pid":"1deebc82d64750dcb38ddf09607cb36e00041332","tid":2099493,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"想轉換環境姐<br />\n又唔係得生存一個選擇"},{"pid":"e9c6467992f507bad1fcacbbb44e32b5865ea156","tid":2099493,"uid":71292,"l